lead_paragraph: New Yorker Kira Kazantsev won the coveted 2015 Miss America Pageant crown on Sunday, a "three-peat" for contenders from the Big Apple.

headline.main: New Yorker Kira Kazantsev 'Happy' to Be Crowned Miss America
